com.lukeleber.scandroid.interpreter

Interface Interpreter

  • All Superinterfaces:
    java.lang.AutoCloseable, java.io.Closeable
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    AbstractInterpreter, ELM327, NativeInterpreter

    public interface Interpreter
extends java.io.Closeable
    The ultimate base class for all interpreter implementations. Interpreters are responsible for providing all of the means required to communicate with a piece of remote hardware, thus acting as a bridge between the android device and the vehicle that is being accessed.
